Package com.edgrantJBusRD

Class Bus

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.edgrantJBusRD.dbjson.Serializable
      • com.edgrantJBusRD.Bus
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Comparable<Serializable>
    public class Bus
extends Serializable
    The Bus class represents a bus in the transportation system. It stores information such as bus name, departure and arrival stations, price, facilities, capacity, and bus type.
